OL,6,FA Newry business owner who has been
OL,7,Fclosed for more than five months has
OL,8,Fbeen asked to repay a #7,500 flooding
OL,9,Fgrant given to her by a local council.
OL,11,FLoretta Gallagher's textile business
OL,12,Foperates on the first floor of a
OL,13,Fbuilding at Sugar House Quay. She told
OL,14,FUTV that the only route into her
OL,15,Fworkspace is via a door which became
OL,16,Finaccessible due to the level of the
OL,17,Fwater when floods hit last November.
