OL,6,FHer business was one of 114 given the
OL,7,Fgrant to help with initial damage.
OL,8,FHowever Newry, Mourne and Down
OL,9,FDistrict Council now says that was
OL,10,Fdone in error and in a letter, has
OL,11,Fasked her to repay the money.
OL,13,F"I applied for the #7,500, I thought I
OL,14,Fdeserved it, I was assessed," she said.
OL,16,F"I was told that I deserved it and
OL,17,Fthen to be told, no you don't because
OL,18,Fof logistics. There has to be more
OL,19,Fthought put into it."
