OL,6,FLoretta added: "I couldn't believe it,
OL,7,FI really couldn't believe it.
OL,9,F"This is a council that knows my
OL,10,Fbusiness, knows me, knows what I do,
OL,11,Fknows that I try and support local
OL,12,Fartists and creatives throughout Newry
OL,13,Fand Mourne."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Newry, Mourne and
OL,16,FDown District Council said it: "does
OL,17,Fnot comment on matters relating to
OL,18,Findividual business applications and
OL,19,Ftherefore no further comment will be
OL,20,Fprovided."
