OL,3,CCouncil asks for flood funding to be
OL,4,Creturned by artist
OL,6,FMany businesses, particularly across
OL,7,FCo Down, were devastated by some of
OL,8,Fthe worst flooding to hit Northern
OL,9,FIreland in years in 2023. Commercial
OL,10,Fpremises in Newry and Downpatrick were
OL,11,Fworst affected.
OL,13,FThe Government allocated #15m in
OL,14,Ffunding for affected businesses as
OL,15,Fwell as rates relief.
OL,17,FIn a second round of funding,
OL,18,Fbusinesses can apply for up to
OL,19,F#100,000 each in an application
OL,20,Fprocess which closes on Friday 22nd
OL,21,FMarch.
